query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS projectDeliveries (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  projectId INT NOT NULL,
  phaseId INT,
  name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  description TEXT,
  type ENUM('document', 'drawing', 'render', 'model', 'report', 'specification', 'other') DEFAULT 'document' NOT NULL,
  dueDate TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  status ENUM('pending', 'in_review', 'approved', 'rejected', 'delivered') DEFAULT 'pending' NOT NULL,
  fileUrl TEXT,
  fileKey VARCHAR(500),
  fileSize INT,
  uploadedAt TIMESTAMP NULL,
  uploadedById INT,
  assignedToId INT,
  priority ENUM('low', 'medium', 'high', 'urgent') DEFAULT 'medium' NOT NULL,
  notificationSent INT DEFAULT 0 NOT NULL,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  updatedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  INDEX projectId_idx (projectId),
  INDEX phaseId_idx (phaseId),
  INDEX status_idx (status),
  INDEX dueDate_idx (dueDate)
);

CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS deliveryApprovals (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  deliveryId INT NOT NULL,
  reviewerId INT NOT NULL,
  status ENUM('approved', 'rejected', 'revision_requested') NOT NULL,
  comments TEXT,
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
  INDEX deliveryId_idx (deliveryId),
  INDEX reviewerId_idx (reviewerId)
);
